{"tid":1301053,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港書展 一齊去三中商（三聯、 中華與商務）打書釘","createTime":"2019-07-09T14:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T01:39:37.000Z","uid":12510,"like":131,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6af8ecc54cce9f758422bb1292a66a0009777ec9","tid":1301053,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">作為一個愛書既連登仔，上至天文下至地理，三中商都有好多好書俾我地睇，一於慢慢去打下書釘，睇岩先好買<br />\n<br />\n三間書局佔地咁多，閒閒地都可以容納一千人到一齊睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"18883fcb50b606524b995db972eb8edbcfad3f1a","tid":1301053,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:06:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9c8294fed51e4476c25f50be3df88c75af76b335","tid":1301053,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:07:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"41fb159d68a6d09baadaa963a0032e4ad436944c","tid":1301053,"uid":179649,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夏天咁熱成日都會幫襯"},{"pid":"bc7f1dc082b4e4f3402360ad5c55f87aeadf0ce1","tid":1301053,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3d8bccbc2d8a62af7d9bf89bb60ca5d9e71700","tid":1301053,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f33d8631ea56dd3ac232f9e2b72528474779e9f","tid":1301053,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"Go go go<br />\n<br />\n睇多D書, 增長知識, 我成日都入商務打書釘, 就黎被人趕出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor